com.dlsc.flexgantt.command.layer

Class DefaultChangeSpreadsheetValueCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dlsc.flexgantt.command.AbstractCommand
      • com.dlsc.flexgantt.command.layer.DefaultChangeSpreadsheetValueCommand
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICommand, Serializable

    public class DefaultChangeSpreadsheetValueCommand
extends AbstractCommand
    A command that will change the value of a spreadsheet cell. This command will only work if the model is an instance of DefaultGanttChartModel and the tree / hierarchy node implements the IGanttChartNode interface. Spreadsheet cells are defined by their time span (x-coordinate) and their tree node (y-coordinate).
    Since:
    2.1
    Author:
    Dirk Lemmermann
    See Also:
